		FTP
=>transfer file to/from remote host
=> client-server model

Runs over TCP
port 20 (control connection)
port 21 (data connection)

cliente precisa de autenticação
cliente consegue fazer browse dos diretorios

Commands
Input				Response
USER <username>		331 Username OK, password re quired
PASS <password>		
LIST (files current dir)	125 Data connection already open; transfer strating
RETR filename (retrieves file) 425 Can't open data connection
STOR (stores file onto server) 425 Error writing file
